	.content
		.cta
			%span I KNEAD THIS!
			%a.btn(title='SIGN UP NOW' href="#") SIGN UP NOW
		%p
			We are currently accepting requests to join our pre-release beta tester group.  There are only a handful of spots left so if you want in, sign up and tell us why you deserve to make our beta team.